I'm not telling everyone my full name, but this is what I do.

Name: UltimateWarriorFan4Ever

Birthday: October 10th

Story status: Not taking any requests for stories. The reasons my updates for new or continued stories are sometimes slow it's because unfortunately, I don't get any time to work on my stories because of all the stuff I'm busy handling one at a time. It's not easy.

Note: If any of you are wondering where my M-rated fics are (most of them smut), it's because they're no longer there due to my MA rated fics being reported by Fanfiction. net support. They sent me an e-mail saying if I did not get rid of my MA rated fics, than my account would be terminated. Unfortunately, I have to follow the site's rules, and I have to abide by them in order to keep my account active. But not to fear everyone, the smutfics you all know and love will now be on Archiveofourown. Which means I will now be posting my hot sexy fics there in order to expand the fanbase. So if you wanna get your dirty urges on, go ahead, but you may have to sign up to the site in order to review my hot smutfics. Sorry, it's AO3 rules. XD

Age: You may ask how old I am, but I may never answer! (MUAHAHAHAHAHAHA) ;D
